      "message": "This is _not_ the icon that you highlighted in the Github issue[1]. You highlighted the \"magnifying glass\" icon that shows/hides the find component. The icon you change here is the search commits icon show inside that component. That one should not be changed:\n1. It is consistent with the view icon of the \"Search\" view, and with icons in the top-level \"Search\" menu and in the tabs in the global \"Search...\" dialog.\n2. We\u0027d end up with two different magnifying glasses in the history page\u0027s toolbar.\n\nThe action highlighted in [1] actually uses **elcl16/find.svg**.\n\nFinally: why is that new SVG so big? As far as I see it\u0027s just a circle and line, both gray. That should give a super-small SVG and not need 515 lines.\n\n[1] https://github.com/eclipse-egit/egit/issues/149",
